<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<%- include('./includes/head.ejs') %>

<body>
  <%- include('./includes/logo.ejs') %>
  <!-- Page Content -->
  <div class="container border border-dark rounded"
    style="margin-top:100px; margin-bottom: 100px; padding: 40px; width: 500px;">
    <!-- Page Heading/Breadcrumbs -->
    <h2>LOGIN</h2>
    <p>Welcome 4989</p>
    <% if(pass == false) { %>
      <p style="color: red;">아이디 또는 비밀번호가 잘못되었습니다.</p>
    <% } %>
    <form method="POST" action="/login">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="usr">ID:</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="usr" name="username">
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="pwd">Password:</label>
        <input type="password" class="form-control" id="pwd" name="password">
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">로그인</button>
    </form>
    <div class="mt-2 mb-4">
      <a href="/signup" class="mr-2">회원가입</a>
      <a href="/find_idpw" class="">아이디/비밀번호 찾기</a>
    </div>
    <div class="container mt-2">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-7">
          사구팔구 회원이 아니신가요?<br/>테스트 계정으로 체험해보세요!
        </div>
        <div class="col ml-auto align-self-center">
          <a href="/guestlogin">
            <button class="btn btn-secondary" type="button">게스트로 체험하기</button>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- /.container -->

  <!-- Footer -->
  <%- include('./includes/footer.ejs') %>

  <!-- Bootstrap core JavaScript -->
  <script src="/vendor/jquery/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/vendor/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
